        "label": "ORG"
      },
      {
        "text": "太平錢",
        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_060_000034",
    "sentence": "由是國家之錢，演迤域中。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_060_000035",
    "sentence": "所以統和出內藏錢，賜南京諸軍司。",
    "entities": [
